UIC’s Excel Center, which includes TRIO, AAAN, Ace, & NASP, within Student Affairs hosted the 1st Annual First-Generation College Student Celebration at UIC (which is part of the 2nd Annual National TRIO First-Generation College Student Celebration Day). The event was open to students, staff, and faculty around campus, and included food, speakers, raffles, and networking activities to celebrate first-generation students.  #CelebrateFirstGen #UICGenOne Website: excellence.uic.edu               Want to learn more about TRIO SSS?  We offer academic coaching, tutorial services, career and graduate school exploration, study room support, and referrals to other services as needed.Click here for more information!   Learn More          Programs        About Us          TRIO Staff          Definitions                        UIC Logo        TRIO       Contact   TRIO Student Support Services  1200 W. Harrison, 2720 SSB Chicago, Illinois 60607  Phone: (312) 996-5046  asp@uic.edu    TRIO Upward Bound  1200 W. Harrison, 2720 SSB Chicago, Illinois 60607  Phone: (312) 996-5046  trioub@uic.edu      Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 